(260, 1, '2012-12-24 11:37:18', '2012-12-24 11:37:18', 'Aztro Media is a Social Media, Online Marketing, Web Solutions and WordPress-developer Company located in Canada. Our aim is to create a website that is a purposive technology hot pot. This is why our branding endeavor is driven with video, image and open source coding technology where users who want to modify a branding message can always return.\r\n\r\nHere is an in-depth coverage of our goals and mission, with follow up service pages.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Mission:</strong>\r\n\r\nTo provide a healthy technological ecosystem for webmasters through versatile social media offerings, cutting edge web solutions and professional online marketing, with an aim to create solutions that open wide the path to success.\r\n\r\nOur mission is in tandem with our method of approaching work on a step-by-step basis. There is the conceptual stage that we call research period on a normal web solutions project. It is succeeded by the wireframe stage, then the prototype phase, followed by the deployment stage, finalizing with testing, monitoring and continuous iteration.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Goals</strong>\r\n\r\nTo grow into an important brick-and-mortar and virtual web solutions-cum-marketing center that drives modern e-commerce.\r\n\r\nWe also aim to reach further into the open source technology milieu where not just flexible applications like HTML5 rule but our own in-house developers’ fruits. This is why we offer prototype plug-ins for WordPress which stem from the core programming language but which we shape to suit the immediate modification needs of the clients’ websites.\r\n\r\nWe also aim to transform our website into a homepage in the style of a customer care center. 24/7 attendance is our drive alongside attending to evanescent needs of customers on SEO like reputation management. We also patch invisible codes that inhibit optimum website visibility on the search indexes.\r\n\r\nAztro Media also aims to de-clutter the Internet off one-time branding esthetics. By this we mean to establish text and visual branding products including logos that stay on for a long time that users can modify rather than axe altogether. We know that many are the times that the software that may have created a past logo is gone with the wind, necessitating users to start from scratch. Instead, we aim to have open source visual and text codes in place for continuous re-branding.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Social Media Roadmap\r\n</strong>Our central objective in social media is to make Facebook pages, applications and content completely beneficial to an e-commerce site. This means that no single page will be there for mere display. We will orientate the client through the potential of the number two of the most visited websites in the world, Facebook, by turning the power of millions into a fortune.\r\n\r\nWe can maintain Social Media through perpetual blog posting, daily updating, instantaneous retraction of bad repute, making announcements, helping gain links and entrenching a Facebook page on the website itself.\r\n\r\nOur goal for web solutions is to make Aztro Media the forum for all software information, ranging from high-end Smartphone operating systems to emerging technologies in the computer world. From android to the iOs and from Windows to Linux, we have a word for each.\r\n\r\nThus, if you need WordPress solutions, or any other fix, come to our brick-and-mortar office in North America or get in touch online.\r\n\r\nHere is a word on each of our services.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Web Solutions</strong>\r\n\r\nWe basically have three sections for our web solutions mandate. These include web design, web development and WordPress.\r\n\r\nWe have a highly creative team of web designers whose main job is to brainstorm, create wireframes and iterate on web portfolios. We have bagged hundreds of clients so far who have something to show for the work of this team that usually works in small unified teams to create original and persuasive WebPages that look appropriate for the particular theme at first glance. Other than committing to innovativeness, we concentrate on basic components of web design. These include creating interactive interfaces that are user-friendly while ensuring they conform to the web development aspect, mapping out the homepage through apt page layout, and optimizing a page through wonderful arrangement of media as well as text.\r\n\r\nOur Web development vaunts the inclusion of more than the usual share of coding, programming and consolidating domains. We research far and wide on how to wire frame, graft prototypes from existing applications or create brand new ones, before assiduously testing and deploying the software product onto the web. While at it, we endeavor to merge the development and design phases by making them interactive in terms of the particular site.\r\n\r\n<strong>WordPress</strong>\r\nWe have a WordPress team that is next to none at making plug-ins work as personalized or custom improvements on core software. The team’s prowess in software mastery is apparent in the handling of plug-ins that gets a project rolling way beyond what can be probably sustained under normal WordPress infrastructure. There are also perpetual prototypes that we construct to keep in <em>par </em>with the end-user’s conceptualization of what a plug-in should be like. Besides, we offer perpetual technical advice to long-term clients as well as provide them with resources to keep their blogs framework going strong under this programming.\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to call us on <strong>0239 245 482</strong>.\r\n\r\nOr drop us a line at <a href="mailto:hello@aztromedia.com" target="_blank"><strong>hello@aztromedia.com</strong></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '156-revision-13', '', '', '2012-12-24 11:37:18', '2012-12-24 11:37:18', '', 156,