(264, 1, '2012-12-21 08:56:48', '2012-12-21 08:56:48', 'Aztro Media<strong> </strong>is proficient in its multi-pronged marketing approach. We are as much branding professionals as we are SEO experts. We also play a critical role in keeping the social media page locked in marketing as much as relevance can allow, knowing well that more than 800 million people today are on Facebook, let alone the other social networking sites. We employ Web 2.0 frameworks like webmaster pages, networking sites and online marketplaces to help the end-user manipulate advertising, optimally. For the umbrella online marketing, we take a level-headed approach to the plethora of promotional opportunities, resources and marketing platforms around the internet. Some of the opportunities that we take advantage of include those of Facebook events, PPC and SEO, while resources include all supportive software like CRM and email list programs. For frameworks, we fall back on the most open source tools including HTML5 that supports multi-device operations like cellular advertising as well as the relatively new Web 2.0. Whether it is branding a logo for a company with a site or just keeping the brand visible via SEO, we will always be there to chip in by way of a helpful word or resource.', 'Marketing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-7', '', '', '2012-12-21 08:56:48', '2012-12-21 08:56:48', '', 17, 'http://www.aztromedia.com/uncategorized/17-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2012-12-27 05:40:37', '2012-12-27 05:40:37', 'The rise of the World Wide Web in the dot com era of the 1990’s as the basic fiber that interconnects information ricocheted on later technologies. One of these is the Web 2.0., apparently an offshoot of the WWW wave only that it bequeaths more innovativeness to the hands of end-users. As such, many networking platforms and interactive portals have enabled users to get in touch more often than before. They no longer have to read third-rate material on sites but can generate it through Facebook, Twitter, Google Webmaster pages and several other interactive forms. It is these platforms that Aztro Media targets in its online marketing campaigns.\n\nOnline marketing for us goes beyond the usual mile. It incorporates video promotions, SEO, cellular advertisement, article submission, creating banners, Social Media Marketing and SEM. To us, digital promotion is something that spawns borders of the traditional web. It is an endeavor that matches the proliferation of Web 2.0 as the user-friendly, intuitive communication framework for the modern man.', 'ONLINE MARKETING', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '265-autosave', '', '', '2012-12-27 05:40:37', '2012-12-27 05:40:37', '', 265, 'http://www.aztromedia.com/uncategorized/265-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
